      • setIsoFile

        public CdromTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setIsoFile(java.lang.String isoFile)
        Path of the image file backing the virtual CD-ROM device. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getType() is CdromTypes.BackingType.ISO_FILE.
        Parameters:
        isoFile - New value for the property.

      • setHostDevice

        public CdromTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setHostDevice(java.lang.String hostDevice)
        Name of the host device backing the virtual CD-ROM device.

        This property will be null if getAutoDetect() is true and the virtual CD-ROM device is not connected or no suitable device is available on the host.
        Parameters:
        hostDevice - New value for the property.

      • setAutoDetect

        public CdromTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setAutoDetect(java.lang.Boolean autoDetect)
        Flag indicating whether the virtual CD-ROM device is configured to automatically detect a suitable host device. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getType() is CdromTypes.BackingType.HOST_DEVICE.
        Parameters:
        autoDetect - New value for the property.

      • setDeviceAccessType

        public CdromTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setDeviceAccessType(CdromTypes.DeviceAccessType deviceAccessType)
        Access type for the device backing. This property is optional and it is only relevant when the value of getType() is one of CdromTypes.BackingType.HOST_DEVICE or CdromTypes.BackingType.CLIENT_DEVICE.
        Parameters:
        deviceAccessType - New value for the property.
